@News We have started the installation of patch 0.12.12.15.3. The installation will take approximately 2 hours, but may be extended if required. The game will not be accessible during this period.

**Optimizations:**
‚óè Decreased possible performance drops on the Flea Market, presets, handbook, stash, skills, and tasks screens;
‚óè Various client optimizations.

**List of changes:**
‚óè Now, when transferring a container needed to complete a task/craft/zone construction in the Hideout, you can only hand over an empty container. When trying to transfer a non-empty container, you will receive a notification saying ‚ÄúYou can't hand over a container with items inside‚Äù;
‚óè Changed the conditions under which Scav bots took a prone position when engaging a player;
‚óè Added new sounds for SCAR-L, different from SCAR-H.

**List of fixes:**
‚óè Fixed an issue due to which shotguns were not dealing damage;
‚óè Fixed an issue causing infinite loading into a raid as a Scav;
Bots can phrase about other Scavs‚Äô dead bodies again;
‚óè Fixed the possibility of rain appearing indoors; 
‚óè Added missing sounds in third person for characters falling from a height/ledge;
Scavs no longer slide in place when changing position;
‚óè Bots no longer walk through the train on the Lighthouse location;
‚óè Bots now equip found weapons on their back instead of putting them in the backpack;
‚óè Keys listed on Flea Market now display durability again;
‚óè Spamming the Caps Lock key while moving no longer lets you move almost silently without a significant slowdown;
‚óè Player uphill movement now looks smooth again in third person;
‚óè Fixed the ability to become invisible while using an AGS grenade launcher as a Scav;
‚óè Fixed the ability to look through the bunker walls on the Reserve location;
‚óè SJ6 TGLabs stimulant now correctly increases maximum stamina again.

