At 16:30 MSK we will begin the installation of an update intended to fix a number of bugs.

We will not stop the game servers, but if you are in a raid during the update installation, your raid may end early. In this case, your character will exit alive with all the gear your character has by that time. You will need to restart and update the game client for the fixes to be applied.

Fixed:
- Grenade explosions without effects or sounds;
- Hangs on loading into a raid at the "awaiting session start" stage;
- Inability to switch the scope mode on the hybrid optics NcSTAR ADO P4 Sniper;
- Incorrect operation of reflex sights shader;
- Various fixes to thermal imagers;
- Various fixes to the UI.

Thank you for understanding! @news

